{"tid":993010,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Motorola 全新摺機專利曝光　外型承襲 RAZR V3 經典設計","createTime":"2019-01-23T14:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T03:37:45.000Z","uid":52215,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d1da922d98c2032897f7c521c824ee0acb5373","tid":993010,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vEH0ZZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vEH0ZZ.jpg&h=72f742ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港 <a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7ff76744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a> 玩生活．樂科技<br />\nMotorola 全新摺機專利曝光　外型承襲 RAZR V3 經典設計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機製造商 Motorola 雖然影響力大不如前，但隨著摺疊熒幕手機的到來，他們亦努力開發有關技術，希望力挽狂瀾。如今，他們更成功取得有關專利，讓外界可先搶先一看他們即將推出的摺疊熒幕手機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲圖為網民製作的CG圖片，並非官方發佈影片（來源：YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n據外國科技網站 91 Mobiles 取得的專利文件顯示，新手機的設計與 2004 年的 RAZR V3 十分相似，而新手機的「下巴」較厚，頂部則採用近年流行的「M字額」設計。機背中央則設有鉸鏈，讓用家摺起手機。雖然就目前的公開圖片可見，手機的前方亦可看見手機的鉸鏈，不過有分析指成品很大機會改進這個設計。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而新手機的機背上方，亦可看見一個尺寸較小的輔助熒幕，設計亦承襲自 RAZR V3 的 CSTN 熒幕位置。讓用家可以立即察看手機的各種推送通知，毋須動輒打開手機，方便日常使用。而在相機亦設有輔助熒幕上方，機背下方則為指紋感應器。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有消息指，有關新手機將使用 Android 系統，最快將於下月限量推出，全球只生產 20 萬部，定價為 1,500 美元（約港幣 HK$11,769 元）。"},{"pid":"5da0c46d10ae515d785b7eafba5d35525624a05a","tid":993010,"uid":12000,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"12k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15e14e8f33ff66cb4f31bc6c935abfae4b6d014","tid":993010,"uid":191352,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:54:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fd4d07d1de53665f8d5c30fd2e6f4fc70c3a961","tid":993010,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ae42cab56bf554606b34856e56950d46112de2","tid":993010,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a79fbaf1e5a2eb6e22caed94f41b72300c032cb","tid":993010,"uid":35180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T00:27:45.000Z","msg":"Lenovo Moto <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a09e50cf2f6d67515f08f44338e919f8d7a7efc","tid":993010,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:03:14.000Z","msg":"12k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1dbc9d20b4549cbd0217a5629bac7043a30f063","tid":993010,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a09e50cf2f6d67515f08f44338e919f8d7a7efc","tid":993010,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:03:14.000Z","msg":"12k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:21:29.000Z","msg":"應該要買22k先啱"},{"pid":"93945a9c09f3cb0980707982ff95baedeb28bbb0","tid":993010,"uid":59910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"大陸化嘅聯想moto 定真係美國嘅motorola 先？"},{"pid":"2dc98c4197955bd225f0e52239ba039d8a6d85e5","tid":993010,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:33:23.000Z","msg":"hello moto"},{"pid":"81870fcd14d126bc8797cdd7b7e8d0c97cec2859","tid":993010,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"點解唔量產"}]}